Class LocalTimePicker

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.scene.control.Skinnable

    public class LocalTimePicker
extends CalendarTimePicker

    LocalTime (JSR-310) picker component. This is an extension of the CalendarPicker adding the new date API JSR-310. Since Calendar will not be removed from the JDK, too many applications use it, this approach of extending CalendarPicker is the most flexible one.
